						<div class="postbody">Hello.  I got most of my programming skills from Nerdy Nights. (<a href="http://nintendoage.com/forum/messageview.cfm?catid=22&amp;threadid=7155" class="postlink">http://nintendoage.com/forum/messageview.cfm?catid=22&amp;threadid=7155</a>)  However, in looking at the sound tutorials, I notice there is no DPCM tutorial.
<br />
<br />Can anyone recommend a good DPCM tutorial, that would implement Nerdy Nights' logic?  One of my ultimate goals is to build a DPCM-based speech engine similar to the one used in Big Bird's Hide and Speak (I don't know whether or not I will be able to implement it in a game I am designing, but it is worth experimenting with...).</div>

