					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">DMC channel has a DAC and a DMA-driven DPCM decoder. You can either use DPCM part to stream DPCM-encoded samples into the DAC, or just use the DAC directly, with well timed code - this allows to play unpacked samples or packed in other format than DPCM.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />My stuff at <a href="http://www.youtube.com/user/shiru8bit" class="postlink">YouTube</a>, <a href="http://soundcloud.com/shiru" class="postlink">SoundCloud</a></div>
