						<div class="postbody">It's compressed PCM, though not in the 1-bit DPCM format that the automatic playback expects. Any format other than DPCM needs pretty much 100% attention from the CPU, and very little animation is possible during playback. You can draw Big Bird's mouth flaps, or a scrolling picture of Rick Astley, but not much more.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

						<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
						<tr valign="middle">
							<td class="gensmall" align="right">
							
							</td>
						</tr>
						</table>
					</td>
				</tr>
				</table>
			</td>
		</tr>

